      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure? This car has been well-loved and is in great shape! It runs super smoothly and has plenty of life left in it. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see this go to a great new home!",
