    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-strung S54 inline-six. This example features a crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and a linear power band optimized by Double VANOS, which has been recently serviced. The chassis remains rigid with a reinforced subframe and upgraded poly-bushings, paired with a limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. The Getrag 6-speed manual offers precise engagement, and the suspension geometry has been maintained with Bilstein dampers. While the aesthetics show minor road-going patina, the drivetrain and cooling system are fully sorted for the demanding enthusiast.",
