      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 is a mechanically sorted example of the E46 platform, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering linear power to a factory GKN limited-slip differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the rod bearings\u2014a critical wear item\u2014have been replaced with treated shells. The chassis maintains its legendary poise through a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry, currently fitted with refreshed bushings for sharpened turn-in. Braking performance is consistent thanks to floating calipers and ventilated rotors. This is a driver-spec machine optimized for throttle-steer capability and peak mechanical engagement.",
